    <a name="5.2.beta1"><h3>Subsonic 5.2.beta1 - Feb 14, 2015</h3></a>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>New:</strong> <a href="sonos.jsp">Sonos</a> integration. Use Subsonic as a music service in Sonos.</li>
